Class CdiMemConfigReader

Show UML class diagram
  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openlcb.cdi.jdom.CdiMemConfigReader

  • public class CdiMemConfigReader
extends Object
    Provide a Reader to the OpenLCB CDI in a node. This first implementation reads the entire data before providing the Reader by call back.
